{"id":799257,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_Ewing","text":"Maria Louise Ewing (born March 27, 1950) is an American opera singer. She sung both soprano and mezzo-soprano roles. She was born in Detroit, Michigan.\nEwing made her debut at the Metropolitan Opera in 1976 in Mozart's \"The Marriage of Figaro\". She starred as Carmen, Dorabella in Mozart's \"Cosi fan tutte\", Salome, the title role in \"L'incoronazione di Poppea\", Marie in Berg's \"Wozzeck\" and Shostakovich's \"Lady Macbeth of Mtsensk\". She also sang and appeared in Henry Purcell's \"Dido and Aeneas\".\nEwing was married to director Peter Hall. Their daughter his actress Rebecca Hall.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Opera","surface_form":"opera","offset":56},{"uri":"Soprano","surface_form":"soprano","offset":84},{"uri":"Mezzo-soprano","surface_form":"mezzo-soprano","offset":96},{"uri":"Detroit","surface_form":"Detroit","offset":133},{"uri":"Michigan","surface_form":"Michigan","offset":142},{"uri":"Metropolitan_Opera","surface_form":"Metropolitan Opera","offset":180},{"uri":"Mozart","surface_form":"Mozart","offset":210},{"uri":"The_Marriage_of_Figaro","surface_form":"The Marriage of Figaro","offset":220},{"uri":"Carmen","surface_form":"Carmen","offset":260},{"uri":"Mozart","surface_form":"Mozart","offset":281},{"uri":"Cosi_fan_tutte","surface_form":"Cosi fan tutte","offset":291},{"uri":"Salome_(opera)","surface_form":"Salome","offset":308},{"uri":"L%27incoronazione_di_Poppea","surface_form":"L'incoronazione di Poppea","offset":335},{"uri":"Alban_Berg","surface_form":"Berg","offset":372},{"uri":"Wozzeck","surface_form":"Wozzeck","offset":380},{"uri":"Shostakovich","surface_form":"Shostakovich","offset":393},{"uri":"Lady_Macbeth_of_the_Mtsensk_District_(opera)","surface_form":"Lady Macbeth of Mtsensk","offset":409},{"uri":"Henry_Purcell","surface_form":"Henry Purcell","offset":465},{"uri":"Dido_and_Aeneas","surface_form":"Dido and Aeneas","offset":482},{"uri":"Peter_Ha